OL,3,CNew pothole-busting machine to fix
OL,4,Ccounty's roads
OL,6,FA new #500,000 pothole-busting machine
OL,7,Fhas arrived in Gloucestershire to help
OL,8,Ffix the county's roads.
OL,10,FThe 13-tonne JCB Pothole Pro will cut
OL,11,Faway damaged sections of the road
OL,12,Fsurface in advance of the repair teams.
OL,14,FThe machine, which was delivered to
OL,15,FGloucestershire County Council this
OL,16,Fweek, will operate in every district
OL,17,Fthis spring.
OL,19,FEight teams will work across the
OL,20,Fcounty in addition to 30 regular
OL,21,Frepair teams.
