OL,3,CNew pothole-busting machine to fix
OL,4,Ccounty's roads
OL,6,FA spray injection patching machine,
OL,7,Fwhich doubles the speed of pothole
OL,8,Frepairs, will also work its way across
OL,9,Fthe county.
OL,11,FThe council revealed last month the
OL,12,Flist of more than 150 roads it is
OL,13,Fplanning to resurface in the current
OL,14,Ffinancial year.
OL,16,FA Gloucestershire County Council
OL,17,Fspokesperson said that now the weather
OL,18,Fhad started to improve they are
OL,19,Fstepping up efforts to tackle potholes
OL,20,Fand deal with the impact of winter
OL,21,Fweather.
