OL,3,CNew pothole-busting machine to fix
OL,4,Ccounty's roads
OL,6,F"The UK's wettest winter for 130 years
OL,7,Fhas put our roads under pressure, but
OL,8,Fwe are trialling new materials and
OL,9,Ftechniques to make better longer-
OL,10,Flasting repairs to Gloucestershire
OL,11,Froads," he told the (LDRS).
OL,13,F"We are continuing to try new methods
OL,14,Fto boost efficiency and ensure we have
OL,15,Fthe right tool for the right job."
OL,17,FDuring the spring and summer, the
OL,18,Fhighways teams will focus on larger
OL,19,Froads, using hot rolled asphalt, the
OL,20,Fmost durable main road material, as
OL,21,Fthis is weather dependent.
